  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ガイ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Guy</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>カイウス</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Caius</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ルビア</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Rubia</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ルーク</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Luke</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>本当にすまなかった。
ルークの無礼は俺が代わりに詫びるから
今日のところは勘弁してくれないか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm really sorry about that.
I apologize on behalf of Luke for his rudeness,
so would it be possible for you to let today go?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>17</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>まあ……あんたがそこまで言うなら</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well... if you're willing to
apologize for him like that and all...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あなたからは誠意が伝わるしね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I can tell you're being sincere about it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ありがとう。
でも、ルークも決して
悪いところばかりじゃないんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thank you.
But Luke isn't by any means just a bad person.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>17</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>んだよ、ガイ！
いつまで手間取ってんだよ。
さっさと帰ろうぜ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What the heck, Guy?!
What are you taking so damn long for?
Let's go home already!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……ホントに？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Really?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ああ……たぶん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah... Probably.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>17</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
